r />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/蔡維邦認為大律師公會應譴責示威者惟大部分人選擇沉默-063825982.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%94%A1%E7%B6%AD%E9%82%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E6%87%89%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%83%9F%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98-063825982.html&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9AqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=48c2aaac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/蔡維邦認為大律師公會應譴責示威者惟大部分人選擇沉默-063825982.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蔡維邦大律師絕對係<strong>自己人</strong>,佢係愛之心恨之切</span></span>想大家停一停林一林,現在局勢<br />\n一日之內這麼多自己人屌我地,why?<br />\n唔割原因是什麼? 林鄭不回應五大訢求? NO<br />\n其實是對<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共產黨恐懼感</span></span>,<br />\n但這是有界限的, 一旦過界<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就極快仆街</span></span>兵敗如山倒<br />\n<br />\n請停止裝修,改成裝飾,獅鳥都要合乎比例(最初話1,2,3,4原則走左邊)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家看在2000多位義士份上忍一忍,我地現在是借下好多債,要連本帶利還的,不會因為大義就無事.運動一輸大家會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即使有普選都要本帶利還.大家請停一停林一林. 我地要一個比現左在好的社會還是差的社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地為了打嬴共產黨而將自己變成共產黨,又為什麼?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />獅鳥要合乎比例啊,這更不是<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請停止裝修</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請停止裝修</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請停止裝修</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻膠和理非真的好快到極限</span></span></span>.....唔割不是沒有原則地唔割不要濫用不要一句<span style=\"color: red;\">鬼做的</span>在沒有証明下阻膠和理非不會接受的<br />\n<br />\n真的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請停止裝修</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"db45a2a16054280a7927fcb0d5f18ecaae6242e8","tid":1655740,"uid":4389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d600608dea092232c7dec82f9fed2374dcbbd445","tid":1655740,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"可能會話我標題黨,可能會屌我,會比N個負評,但我真係想大家睇一睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191015/20787092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191015%2F20787092&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9AqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=619a9cda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191015%2F20787092&h=2ecc04c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191015/20787092</a><br />\n蘋論︰ 對「逆權運動」的一些提醒 - 盧峯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/社評/article/20191015/s00003/1571077381550/社評-炸彈登場獨狼割警頸-暴力不遏勢毁掉香港\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95%2Farticle%2F20191015%2Fs00003%2F1571077381550%2F%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95-%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4%E7%8D%A8%E7%8B%BC%E5%89%B2%E8%AD%A6%E9%A0%B8-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%8F%E5%8B%A2%E6%AF%81%E6%8E%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9AqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=f1f6f3fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95%2Farticle%2F20191015%2