 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即使有普選都要本帶利還.大家請停一停林一林. 我地要一個比現左在好的社會還是差的社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地為了打嬴共產黨而將自己變成共產黨,又為什麼?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />獅鳥要合乎比例啊,這更不是<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請停止裝修</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請停止裝修</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請停止裝修</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻膠和理非真的好快到極限</span></span></span>.....唔割不是沒有原則地唔割不要濫用不要一句<span style=\"color: red;\">鬼做的</span>在沒有証明下阻膠和理非不會接受的<br />\n<br />\n真的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請停止裝修</span></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"你去仆街死啦，分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00334f340568eede6e8231320e4aea3bbde5c1df","tid":1655740,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"呢度好有趣。<br />\n接受唔到嘅人就話係鬼做。<br />\n接受到嘅人就話係手足。<br />\n<br />\n唔會割，但又冇普遍共識方向